            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>cooled rice</strong> and the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>remaining lime juice</strong> and a little drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your<strong> brown rice salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
